      "card": "card.knight",
      "role": "Protector",
      "lore": "A Templar of Elara's dawnlit order, Rowan bears a kite shield and an oath to keep her light standing when the dark presses close.",
      "profileBio": "Rowan Valeguard once served Brindlemarket's old watch, but his oath found sharper purpose at Elara Sunmere's shrine. Initiated into her dawnlit order as a Templar protector, he carries a blue-gold kite shield marked with sanctuary stars and holds the line wherever her healing light must reach. Rowan still speaks with the plain steadiness of a village guard; only the armor changed. His promise did not. He walks beside Elara so her hands can mend, guide, and bless without fear of what waits in the dark.",
