      "card": "card.priest",
      "role": "Healer",
      "lore": "A shrine keeper who learned to fold dawnlight into practical miracles after the village roots began to darken.",
      "profileBio": "Elara Sunmere keeps the first lamp lit at Brindlemarket's hillside shrine, tending prayers before dawn and wounds after dusk. When Moonroot Hollow began pressing its shadow into the village roots, she learned to fold dawnlight into practical miracles: mending torn flesh, cleansing poison, and wrapping allies in a veil warm enough to steady their courage. Gentle by habit and stubborn by oath, Elara walks with the party so no one has to face the dark without a hand to guide them back.",
