      "lore": "A runaway academy scholar chasing Moonroot crystals, Cassian would rather be right than safe, which worries everyone else.",
      "profileBio": "Cassian Runevale left the academy with more questions than permission. Moonroot crystals fascinate him, and the Hollow's impossible geometry keeps tempting him closer to danger than the party would prefer. Behind the dry remarks and perfect posture is a caster who trusts precision, theory, and one very bright arcane answer when the dark refuses to move.",
