      "lore": "A white-haired cat girl scout who knows every roofline in Brindlemarket and every rumor about Moonroot Hollow.",
      "profileBio": "Nia Quickwhisker knows the village from roof tiles to cellar locks, and she has opinions about all of it. She scouts ahead by moonlight, marks safe paths, and returns with pockets full of useful things she insists were unattended. Quick, watchful, and hard to corner, Nia keeps the party moving before trouble realizes it has been spotted.",
